t;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生表示将帮助富迪家人实现更大的梦想&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生在众人热烈的掌声、欢呼声和呐喊声中来到会场激情演讲。他首先代表富迪公司热烈欢迎全国各地赶来的家人，并表示衷心感谢。他表示：富迪公司风雨中不断前行，靠的就是这样一群有相同使命感的家人不离不弃。富迪公司有今天的成就，是因为无数富迪家人的支持和付出，是所有富迪人与他一起奋斗在市场的第一线的成果。展望2017年，富迪公司将会制定出更多、更先进的商业模式，开发更具有竞争力和市场前景的产品，帮助富迪家人实现更大的梦想。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;“没有做不到，只有想不到！富迪公司已经走过了十多年的发展历程，我们现在拥有一流的硬件设施和相同的价值观、共同的使命感，接下来我们将一起携手前进，怀着阳光健康的心态，创造新的辉煌！”陈怀德先生诚挚邀请新人加入富迪大家庭，成为梦想的追随者，同时鼓励资深经销商们积极传播富迪新的梦想。他充满激情的精彩演讲，引来了一阵又一阵雷鸣般的掌声和欢呼声。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170419/1492578449482800.png&quot; title=&quot;1492578449482800.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;关静女士激情演绎&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;今后营销的定位、目标与市场启动发展规划&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 22.5pt; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 11pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;说明会上，关静女士闪亮登场，她侃侃而谈，讲述自己十七年的职业经历，她真情满满地叙述了与富迪结缘的初衷和感动，更将富迪公司无私奉献、大爱无疆的善举表达得淋漓尽致，感恩之情溢于言表，感染着在座的每一位富迪家人，也深深感动了现场的每一位朋友。围绕富迪公司2017年营销的定位与目标、融合拓展、科技演进、产品优势、市场启动发展规划等内容，关静女士进行了详尽的阐述。她表示：未来的财富一定掌握在那些有理想、有智慧、有准备的人手中。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170419/1492578460680825.png&quot; title=&quot;1492578460680825.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Tahoma;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-siz