-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;，顶峰相见”为主题的富迪健康科技产品项目招商会在美丽的河南省会郑州隆重举行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;一日破晓，有童者数十人，起于鸡鸣&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;当是时，东方微明，白露未晞&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;不辜负这一天的清晨&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;连续八届荣膺“中国十大慈善家”、中国经济十大商业领袖、中国扶贫开发协会副会长、全国工商联美容化妆品业商会副会长、民建中央对外联络部副部长、广东省第十二届人大代表、富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生，长成国际商学院执行院长江南先生&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;富迪健康科技有限公司河南分公司总经理李宗军先生，与富迪资深经销商丁文凯先生、牛双旺先生、张丽梅女士、郝爱军女士、张文魁先生等&lt;/span&gt;300&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;多位来自全国各地的企业领袖、商界翘楚、金融大咖及热情似火的富迪家人莅临会场，他们用激情互动全场，共同见证了这场盛会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986023600615.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986023600615.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生在众人期待下信步走来&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;领航人陈怀德先生在众人热烈的掌声、欢呼声中信步走到舞台中央，过程中不忘与家人们微笑相视，握手问候。他首先代表富迪公司热烈欢迎全国各地赶来的家人，并表示衷心感谢。他就富迪公司推出的新产品，向与会的市场精英与家人们作了详细的讲解。他说“新的产品作为未来的趋势与直销的完美结合是一次伟大的创举，也是有卓识远见的人们把握时机，赢得新财富的伟大契机。新的项目融合拓展、科技演进、拥抱世界，未来已来！随着互联网发展的时间越长、生活形态越来越数字化，实体经济与数字经济趋势正彼此冲击并融合。未来的财富一定掌握在那些有理想、有智慧、有准备的人手中。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986037205066.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986037205066.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生温情演讲&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;他表示：富迪公司风雨中不断前行，靠的就是这样一群有相同使命感的家人不离不弃。富迪公司有今天的成就，是因为无数富迪家人的支持和付出，是所有富迪人与他一起奋斗在市场的第一线的成果。展望&lt;/span&gt;2017&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;年，富迪公司将会制定出更多、更先进的商业模式，开发更具有竞争力和市场前景的产品，帮助富迪家人实现更大的梦想。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;他承诺“富迪伸出的手一定是最有责任的”。他会用自己生命的全部力量支持家人梦想的达成。随后陈怀德先生在深情的回望了自己的心路历程及艰辛的创业经历后，以高瞻远瞩的雄才大略，用专业规范的金融资本理论剖析了富迪公司的商业规划，让全体家人看到了未来的美好愿景。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986057754130.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986057754130.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;江南老师向大家介绍了富迪公司的价值志愿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&qu