; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;产品说明会，于&lt;/span&gt;5月27-28日在广东佛山成功举办。两天一夜，畅享精英盛宴，舞台释放自我。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;连续八届荣膺&lt;/span&gt;“中国十大慈善家”、中国经济十大商业领袖、中国扶贫开发协会副会长、全国工商联美容化妆品业商会副会长、民建中央对外联络部副部长、广东省第十二届人大代表、富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生，长成国际商学院执行院长江南老师，携同资深经销商欧舟先生、丁文凯先生、李何昊先生、李旭先生、贺非凡先生、陈宥豪先生、闫思诺女士、陈兰蒂女士、余心薇女士、李政沅先生等近千名富迪家人共同见证了此次盛会的成功举办举行。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;一轮炫彩夺目的开场灯光秀、一场震撼心弦的锣鼓表演过后，主持人激昂而婉转地介绍现场领导，并隆重宣布富迪&lt;/span&gt;“睿变2017，精英盛宴”产品说明会正式开始。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986812707076.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986812707076.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生在热烈的掌声和欢呼声中信步走来&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;伴随着一曲气势恢宏、铿锵有力的旋律响起，陈怀德先生信步走来，此时全场欢声雷动，掌声、欢呼声和呐喊声经久不绝。这样的热情场景陈怀德先生历经过无数次，但每次他都表示由衷感激，因为它是家人们给的信任，递的温暖。在大家的簇拥下，在这之前的所有疲惫，都显得不是事。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986824808554.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986824808554.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生鼓励富迪家人放大梦想、践行梦想&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生说：&lt;/span&gt;“富迪公司能取得现在的辉煌，除了积极响应国家‘大众创业，万众创新’的号召，不断探索新的商业模式外，主要是依靠着这样一群生死与共，有相同使命感的家人不离不弃的跟随。没有你们，我成功不了。”陈怀德先生真情表白，“梦想如此美丽，但要脚踏实地去践行，放大你们的梦想，富迪会加大你们的收益。”并承诺，他会用自己生命的全部，全力以赴支持所有家人达成梦想。他的声音响彻大堂，充满激情。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生在深情地回望了自己的心路历程及艰辛的创业经历后，以高瞻远瞩的雄才大略，用专业规范的金融资本理论剖析了富迪公司的商业规划，让全体家人看到了未来的美好愿景。在演讲的最后，陈怀德先生鼓励更多人融入富迪这个友爱的大家庭，&lt;/span&gt;“富迪大舞台，有梦你就来！”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170609/1496986835300818.png&quot; title=&quot;1496986835300818.png&quot; alt=&quot;blob.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;江南老师详细阐述公司经营理念&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;H