司发展历程及近期经营状况，并就当前遇到的实际问题及解决思路进行汇报。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20170706/1499316408619231.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1499316408619231.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;1.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;区政府领导与陈怀德胡静伉俪合影&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;赖志鸿对我司秉持着“责任、担当、付出、合作、共赢、高效”的企业方针，和大爱的文化理念及“永远把帮助别人放在第一位”的崇尚价值观表示高度赞赏，感谢陈怀德先生多年来对侨商会作出的贡献，并对公司的发展及对地方经济作出的成绩予以充分肯定，鼓励我司在市场竞争中进一步做大做强，稳健经营，向“打造一流直销企业”“打造更大的就业平台，帮助更多的人成功”的企业愿景不断努力。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生对政府一直以来对我司的关心、指导和支持表示由衷感谢，并表示今后将一如既往地坚持发展、不断创新，提升企业核心竞争力，为区域经济乃至全国做出更大贡献，绝不辜负政府对我司的信赖，以实际行动回馈社会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:10:\"updatetime\";s:10:\"1497420300\";s:6:\"sysadd\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"modelid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"username\";s:5:\"admin\";s:8:\"position\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"inputtime\";s:10:\"1499316426\";s:6:\"userid\";s:1:\"0\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"953\";s:3:\"url\";s:34:\"/index.php?c=content&a=show&id=953\";s:9:\"listorder\";s:1:\"0\";}');
