ot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;富迪领航人陈怀德先生亲自接待考察团一行，向客人介绍了公司的经营情况，并对公司未来的远景规划作了深入的讲解。他说着：在商业运营模式上，富迪一直秉承着创新与务实、数据与理论相结合的严谨态度，不做纸上谈兵，只做务实可行；在慈善道路上，坚守大爱为本，既施人以鱼，也施人以渔，但更多的是在平台上帮助更多人走向成功，这是富迪意识上最大的慈善。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171106/1509941587172202.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1509941587172202.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;22.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;司博郡先生向到访客人讲解卫生巾优势&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;用户的满意是富迪的营销标准！专业化、个性化、差异化，将最优质的产品介绍给用户，更好满足我们用户的需求，呈现最佳理想化，一起共富行，是我们合作的追求。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;张旭辉先生表示“富迪公司能在激烈且大多雷同的直销市场竞争中，独树一帜，不忘初心，保持不断向前的动力，创造出由神话到奇迹再到传奇的华丽转变，实属不易。今天的参观，有倾叹、有折服，更多的是肯定。在未来，诚挚的希望能与富迪有合作，在新领域下，携手共同取得辉煌的成绩。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171106/1509941596106015.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1509941596106015.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;23.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171106/1509941607637262.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1509941607637262.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;24.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;佛山高明工厂&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:10:\"updatetime\";s:10:\"1506492120\";s:6:\"sysadd\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"modelid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"username\";s:5:\"admin\";s:8:\"position\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"inputtime\";s:10:\"1509941621\";s:6:\"userid\";s:1:\"0\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"982\";s:3:\"url\";s:34:\"/index.php?c=content&a=show&id=982\";s:9:\"listorder\";s:1:\"0\";}');
