nt; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;31&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;日下午，“肽精彩”产品说明会暨华东地区启动大会，在充满园林艺术风情的江苏江阴市举办。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;连续八届荣膺“中国十大慈善家”、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;中国经济十大商业领袖、中国扶贫开发协会副会长、全国工商联美容化妆品业商会副会长、民建中央对外联络部副部长、广东省第十二届人大代表、富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生，携钟厚华先生、徐石金先生、范靖烨先生等市场领导人，及近&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;800&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;位富迪家人参加了会议，共同探讨富迪肽的发展进程，以及它带来的发展模式及对未来的展望与期待，会议在一场激情震撼的龙鼓表演后盛大开场。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生在致辞中对来宾们的到来表示热烈的欢迎和衷心的感谢，他说：“今年带着富迪肽的‘第三次涅槃重生’奋斗历程不寻常，满怀豪情向未来，我们之所以取得这样的成绩，除了抓住大众创业，万众创新的新时代发展要领，就是有这样一群生死与共，有相同使命感的家人不离不弃的跟随。没有你们，富迪成功不了。”在感谢大家的同时，他也正气凛然地激励着富迪家人们，要成为拥有‘问苍茫大地，谁主沉浮’的胆识和‘数风流人物，还看今朝’的气魄的人。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171106/1509944390199045.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1509944390199045.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;56.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生精彩致辞&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p st