00%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;“&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;级质量诚信企业”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;，并确定授予&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;“质量诚信企业”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;牌匾。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;富迪健康科技有限公司是一家集科研、开发、生产、销售、服务、培训于一体的现代化大型直销企业，自&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;1994&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;年在上海成立以来，始终秉持着“我们所做的一切都是为了爱”的文化理念，以领先科技研发尖端产品，专注绿色健康生活，坚持诚信投资、守法经营，不忘立足慈善，积极履行社会责任。也因此得到了政府相关部门的充分肯定和社会各界的广泛认可。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;中国企业质量诚信网，是国家质量监督检验检疫总局主管、中国检验检疫学会主办，是中国检验检疫学会质量诚信建设委员会承办的&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;反映中国企业质量诚信&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;的工作平台。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;“中国企业质量诚信网”根据&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;“企业承诺、数据说话、社会评价、统一标准”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;的原则，联合&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;301&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;所制定学会团体标准《企业质量诚信评定准则》，依据统一的标准，全面、实时、动态、真实地反映企业质量信用信息，把控企业质量高标准高信誉，推动质量强国建设。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171113/1510558814825687.jpg&quot; style=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;1510558814825687.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171113/1510558814488675.jpg&quot; style=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;1510558814488675.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20171113/1510558814647385.jpg&quot; style=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;1510558814