span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;今年，参加的选手主要有历届校友、董事、全校师生、家长，其中就包括了85届广雅毕业生、广雅杰出校友、富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生。他重返校园，与大家一同热跑五公里为母校贺寿。赛事设有精英跑、欢乐跑、运动嘉年华、慈善筹款四个环节。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;早晨八点，钟楼前已是热闹非凡。动感的音乐和&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;绚烂的阳光&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;，热身等待检录的选手和忙碌的工作人员，赶来加油助威的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;家长、朋友&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;和手持相机的摄影&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;师&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;......富迪的“绿”、跑道的“红”、选手们的“蓝”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;在诺大的操场上形成一道道&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;炫彩的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;风景，成为广雅的一抹亮色&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;让校园变得&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;热情洋溢、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;活力四射&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515045858674432.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515045858674432.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;4.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生跑过终点&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;比赛还未开始，选手们已经聊得热火朝天，对比赛似乎都显得斗志满满，天气预报本是阴雨的天空，在早晨的九时迎来了阳光明媚。伴随着钟声的响起，赛道前，一张张充满期待和兴奋的脸庞，看到熟悉的面孔互相挥手，陈怀德先生融身其中，亦感慨道：青春本色，感恩重温于此。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515045865309265.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515045865309265.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;5.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生接受广东电视台的采访&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生接受广东电视台采访时回忆到“从前在广雅读书时，每天跑四公里，这片土地像是早已与我融为一体。跑步的积极向上心态也影响并伴随着我走过读书、创业中艰难的一路，如果说人生是场马拉松，它更像是一场自己与自己的战役。通过马拉松运动能了解自己的体能、意志和前进的目标，更重要的是锻炼了身体。有态度的前行才能不断克服坎坷，勇攀高峰！”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515045870807905.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515045870807905.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;6.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生接受在校学妹的采访&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 22pt; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;面对后辈学妹的提问，亦提出了忠言：健康的心态、向上的学习心态、不怕吃苦不怕累的精神是未来成功的要素。同时，鼓励同学们多参加到这类活动中来，感受一场酷似人生长跑的内涵和魅力。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515045885457769.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515045885457769.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;7.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;长跑之后校友们都来品尝我们的“富迪肽”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;在富迪公司的服务点前，挤满了雅马跑的校友们，有咨询的，有品尝的，络绎不绝，陈怀德先生不厌其烦亲自解答。当他们了解到运动之后补充“富迪肽”，对消除肌肉疼痛会有良好的效果时，他们更是大口大口地喝了起来，并叫来更多的校友，服务点人潮汹涌，一千多份宣传单张几乎不够派发。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515045890448744.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515045890448744.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;8.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&q