t; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;日，由本质传媒主办，世界直销（中国）研究中心承办，直销口碑网、《中国直销》杂志、直销百科网、《直销参考》手机报联合承办的以“行稳致远”为主题的第十三届（&lt;/span&gt;2017&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;）中国直销风云榜在重庆圆满落幕，连续三届荣膺中国十大慈善家、广东省营养健康产业协会副会长、广东省富迪慈善基金会理事长胡静女士代表出席，与来自商务部及重庆市相关领导、业界权威专家、企业高管、系统领袖以及市场精英等&lt;/span&gt;4000&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;余人齐聚山城，共同见证中国直销界高规格、高品质、好口碑的堪称“行业奥斯卡”荣耀盛典。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515046899599923.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515046899599923.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;35.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;胡静女士上台致辞&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;此次盛典，获奖者由直销口碑网上通过全民推荐、大众评选和综合评定，以候选者在&lt;/span&gt;2017&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年度的相关指标为基础，借鉴国际经验，结合企业或个人在这一年的实际情况以及对社会的贡献度来考评，最后选出。&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生凭借专业、厚实、诚心、创新、慈善的精神品质，精准的前瞻方向，专业的领导决策能力，平易近人、待人实诚的人格魅力荣膺“&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;2017&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年度中国直销风云企业家”和“价值企业家”，富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生荣获“价值经理人”称号，富迪小分子肽荣登产品榜，富迪市场精英领导人钟厚华先生获得“卓越创业领袖”奖，富迪纵横系统取得“价值系统”奖等数个奖项。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515046908178176.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515046908178176.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;36.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;胡静女士上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;胡静女士作为富迪慈善基金会理事长，也作为陪伴陈怀德先生走过富迪风起云涌的“台前幕后”支持者，她致辞时首先代表陈怀德先生、代表富迪公司诚挚地感谢到中国直销风云榜颁发的奖项，她说道：“言必行，行必果”是陈怀德先生做人处事的准则，他不仅这样要求自己，也同样要求自己的团队。在直销企业运营上，最重要的就是“以人为本”，真正做到逼近消费者内心，在这一点，富迪从产品、市场服务、用户体验、人性化模式和理念多方面兼顾，做到尽善尽美。未来，富迪会愈加努力，走高标准、高品质、接地气的服务路线，也希望大家继续给予关爱与支持。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515046920500029.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515046920500029.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;37.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生荣获“价值经理人”称号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;11&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年来，富迪公司以“一步一个脚印”稳固发展的心态，行稳、走直、心诚、志定，主题“行稳·致远”也定是富迪践行且必成的阵势。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;本次会议获得了重庆电视台、中国消费者报、天府早报、重庆晨报、重庆晚报、重庆商报、华龙网、大渝网、直销博客网、直销道道网、中国直销网、直销人网、直销头条网、反传销网、直销快评网、直销堂网、第一直销网等媒体的大力支持。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:10:\"updatetime\";s:10:\"1512634800\";s:6:\"sysadd\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"modelid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"username\";s:5:\"admin\";s:8:\"position\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"inputtime\";s:10:\"1515046951\";s:6:\"userid\";s:1:\"0\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"999\";s:3:\"url\";s:34:\"/index.php?c=content&a=show&id=999\";s:9:\"listorder\";s:1:\"0\";}');
INSERT INTO `fn_sb` VALUES ('66', 'content_add', 'a:35:{s:5:\"catid\";s:2:\"30\";s:5:\"title\";s:81:\"喜报！富迪一举斩获第十三届中国直销产业发展论坛多项大奖\";s:8:\"keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:42:\"/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047039571236.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:300:\"12月10日，由中国新闻文化促进会主办，海畴传媒集团精心筹备的，被誉为“直销指南针·行业达沃斯”第十三届中国直销产业发展论坛在北京九华山庄盛大启幕，富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生代表富迪公司出席了...\";s:6:\"prices\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"kinds\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size2\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size3\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size4\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size5\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size6\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size7\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size8\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size9\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"fn_add_introduce\";s:1:\"1\";s:19:\"fn_introcude_length\";s:3:\"200\";s:13:\"fn_auto_thumb\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"fn_down_image\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"hits\";s:1:\"0\";s:11:\"select_time\";s:10:\"1512980880\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"relation\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"content\";s:14217:\"&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;月10日，由中国新闻文化促进会主办，海畴传媒集团精心筹备的，被誉为“直销指南针· 行业达沃斯”第十三届中国直销产业发展论坛在北京九华山庄盛大启幕，富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生代表富迪公司出席了此次论坛。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047039571236.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047039571236.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;38.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生代表富迪公司上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;各级地方政府主管直销与经贸的相关领导、一百多家直销企业高管代表、人民网、新华网、央视网40多家媒体与会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;在“风云·2017亚太直销行业总结表彰颁奖盛典”上，组委会的专家们通过对各个企业、系统及个人的严格甄选和专业评定评选出权威奖项，富迪一举斩获四项大奖，分别是：&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生荣膺“2017亚太地区直销行业杰出企业家珠穆朗玛奖”（顶级行业大奖）；吴文广先生荣膺“2017亚太直销杰出管理专家”；“富迪肽”荣获“2017亚太地区直销行业消费者最佳口碑直销产品”；富迪公司荣获“2017亚太地区直销行业最佳创业基地”，载誉而归。&lt;/strong&gt;珠穆朗玛奖是本届论坛在行业内首次推出的顶级行业大奖，以期弘扬直销人的奋斗精神，定义行业新标准。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047047259044.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047047259044.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;39.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生代表富迪公司上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;在新时代下，面对国际环境新变化和国内发展新要求，各个直销企业都在重新思考未来发展问题，就如何深入实施创新发展，推动企业优化结构，不断提高质量、效益和竞争力，吴文广先生在论坛上也提出了看法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;随着新直销的井喷式增长和大健康产业的快速崛起，富迪凭借一款突破性产品“富迪肽”直冲大健康行业，在产品研发、品质服务上独具匠心，另辟蹊径，并以此为契机，整合资源、优化配置，开创新模式，顺势而力促发展，乘势而上求突破，初心未改，大爱至上，一路高歌猛进，实现第三次腾飞跨越式发展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047053732774.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047053732774.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;40.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生代表富迪公司上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;论坛举办，直销界睥睨天下的精英将领们各抒己见，相互碰撞。为一个共同话题，未来行业发展战略最佳方向；为一个共同目标，直销举步，巅峰之上。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;论坛结束，我们收获了不只是看到群英荟萃，群贤毕集的场面，高瞻明睿的智慧碰撞；也不只是集过去经验，谈未来创新、发展与融合，更多的是如何在国家合作共赢的大政方针下，共建共享、共同发展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047060425545.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047060425545.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;41.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生代表富迪公司上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;这天，我们细数行业收获，总结因果利弊，感叹风雨兼程，见证历年辉煌，探讨发展方向。在各方高屋建瓴下，&lt;/span&gt;2017&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年为直销行业创造一个个新成绩，一次次突破新高度，今天我们感谢为过去留下汗水的每个人，未来，我们愈加对登上直销云霄之巅心怀憧憬，在这条道路上不忘初心，砥砺前行！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:10:\"updatetime\";s:10:\"1512980880\";s:6:\"sysadd\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"modelid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"username\";s:5:\"admin\";s:8:\"position\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"inputtime\";s:10:\"1515047153\";s:6:\"userid\";s:1:\"0\";s:2:\"id\";s:4:\"1000\";s:3:\"url\";s:35:\"/index.php?c=content&a=show&id=1000\";s:9:\"listorder\";s:1:\"0\";}');
INSERT INTO `fn_sb` VALUES ('67', 'content_add', 'a:35:{s:5:\"catid\";s:2:\"30\";s:5:\"title\";s:100:\"越秀区人大代表莅临我司参观考察 留下“开拓创新，践行务实”的高度评价\";s:8:\"keywords\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:42:\"/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047326856127.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:301:\"12月13日，越秀区人大代表赴我司参观考察，莅临的人大代表有：越秀区人大常委、侨工委主任张铧，广州市人大代表、广州市十大杰出青年雷建威，广州市越秀区人大常委、区侨工委副主任王东，广州市人大代表、广州市伊斯...\";s:6:\"prices\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"kinds\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size2\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size3\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size4\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size5\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size6\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size7\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size8\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"size9\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"fn_add_introduce\";s:1:\"1\";s:19:\"fn_introcude_length\";s:3:\"200\";s:13:\"fn_auto_thumb\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"fn_down_image\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"hits\";s:1:\"0\";s:11:\"select_time\";s:10:\"1513240260\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"relation\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"content\";s:9294:\"&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;12&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;13&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;日，越秀区人大代表赴我司参观考察，莅临的人大代表有：越秀区人大常委、侨工委主任张铧，广州市人大代表、广州市十大杰出青年雷建威，广州市越秀区人大常委、区侨工委副主任王东，广州市人大代表、广州市伊斯兰教协会副会长张建君，越秀区人大常委戴丽萍，广州市人大代表、广州市佛教协会副会长释广盛法师、广州市越秀区常委、人大代表李影主任，越秀区侨商会副会长、越秀区人大代表李创华。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;此次人大代表莅临富迪视察工作，是为了进一步调研富迪与健康产业的发展情况，给予更大力度的支持工作。受富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生委托，富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生亲自接待，并由富迪工作人员讲解公司文化及运营理念。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047326856127.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047326856127.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;42.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;人大代表考察团一行在我司合影留念&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生对人大代表一行的到来表示热烈欢迎，并对多年来各人大代表对富迪的关心与支持，表示衷心感谢。他介绍了富迪公司近况，生产经营、项目模式和经济产业链等情况。&lt;/span&gt;2017&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年，随着“一带一路”政策推出和大健康产业的兴盛，富迪紧跟国家发展战略步伐，以迅雷不及掩耳之势跻身直销及健康产业榜样级企业。接下来，富迪也会在适应经济新常态下，立足绿色健康产业，不断加强创新，拓展企业发展新路径。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047334105458.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047334105458.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;43.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;长成国际商学院教育总监介绍公司产业链&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180104/1515047344552801.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1515047344552801.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;44.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;工作人员向人大代表一行介绍公司的企业文化理念&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;富迪工作人员向来访的代表介绍了富迪多产品结构、多产业架构、多创新模式、服务个性化等企业基本运营模式。大健康产业是国家十分重视的，解决好健康医疗问题是国家快速发展的根本。新产品“富迪肽”核心技术，以“小分子、快溶解、快吸收、无化学”食品优势冲破传统技术的局限，得到健康产业专家一致认可，由此展开的直销新模式也帮助了许多创业者更快接近预期的成功。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\";s:10:\"updatetime\";s:10:\"1513240260\";s:6:\"sysadd\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"modelid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"username\";s:5:\"admin\";s:8:\"position\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"inputtime\";s:10:\"1515047358\";s:6:\"userid\";s:1:\"0\";s:2:\"id\";s:4:\"1001\";s:3:\"url\";s:35:\"/index.php?c=content&a=show&id=1001\";s:9:\"listorder\";s:1:\"0\";}');
