background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;由富迪公司众仁德系统联合陕西三八妇乐科技股份有限公司、成川国际系统、仁和无极国际系统出品制作代表直销创业精神的微电影《来生还做直销人》，于20号首映登场，影片讲述着直销人的心声和经历。在国家鼓励双创的今天，“草根创业”、自主创业人群渴望更多让自己发声的舞台。这部从侧面反映中国直销人成功创业的艰辛的影片，相信在正式上线、大众公映后，将会引起又一轮舆论热潮。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;该电影自从在第十三届世界华人直销大会上发布了预告片后，引起了社会大众的重点关注。视频发布不到一个星期，点击量突破25万，该片的题材、内容及故事情节更是成为网友们追逐的热点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri;&quot;&gt;“金犁奖”颁奖盛典 富迪斩获四大奖项&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;21日晚，第九届“金犁奖”颁奖典礼盛大启幕。推崇创业标杆，讴歌开犁闯关的“金犁奖”创设于2009年，因紧随“双创”潮流而受到公共组织、媒体、企业家以及创业者的广泛关注。“金犁奖”用传媒的公信力，用群众的影响力，向世界发出了属于中国自主创业者的声音。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;经过为期数月的大众网络投票、媒体和专家评审团评审，第九届“金犁奖”中，富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生荣膺“2017中国品牌影响力企业家”、富迪健康科技有限公司荣获“2017年度最具合作价值创业平台”、广东省富迪慈善基金会获得“2017年度公益慈善项目”、富迪小分子肽荣获“2017年度创新产品”等四项大奖，富迪当之无愧是直销业界的宠儿。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mar