ly: 宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;7&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;日，“砥砺奋进，为爱前行”富佑集团&lt;/span&gt;2018&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;年发展战略会议成功举办，会议探讨的是集团发展导向一场重要的战略布局规划，也是互联网&lt;/span&gt;+&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;大健康产业&lt;/span&gt;+&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;直销体系建设的重要内容，旨在深入实施大健康产业与我司发展方向融合发展战略，会议主要是结合直销发展趋势，围绕富迪企业在未来应该如何做好展开。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生表示：富迪在&lt;/span&gt;2018&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;也将重心放于健康产业及产品、平台、服务联合发展的品牌建设上，抵制以药养医，将预防落到实处。政策与需求对富迪当下形势都是有利的，为此我们推行了更具创新型意义、更贴合当下互联网发展的商业模式，其中增设“全民补肽，富迪在行动”、“全民补肽&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;免费试喝”系列活动，特设区县代理、配送中心、服务网点费用补贴政策，以及免费试喝产品补贴政策等等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;这些年，我们花大精力投入技术研发，专注生产，就是为了能让消费者简单有效地守护健康、呵护美丽，轻松便捷地增添活力，在“科技造就爱”“生命健康管理”理念的指引下，投入巨资优化生产基地建设并引进国际先进设备，形成了多个生产基地优势互补的格局。目前富迪已经在公司建设、市场开拓、品牌提升等各个方面取得了良好成绩，为未来发展奠定坚实基础。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180205/1517810754216262.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1517810754216262.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;8.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; wo