x !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180205/1517815598569550.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1517815598569550.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;39.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生，叶根女士，袁伟先生，陈文宇先生和丁文凯先生参为富迪四川分公司重装开业剪彩&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生，广州大爱企业管理咨询有限公司执行总裁叶根女士，富迪健康科技有限公司健康管理学院执行院长袁伟先生，四川分公司经理周预博先生，以及资深经销商陈文宇先生、丁文凯先生、乔峰先生、周大福先生、张皓成先生、闫思诺女士等200多位富迪家人欢聚一堂，不畏严寒，与“肽”暖冬。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;富迪在全国各地建立了几十家分公司，市场业务遍及全国。随着富迪四川分公司重装剪彩完美开业，宣示着又一块区域链的重塑建立，也将迎来更广阔的明天。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180205/1517811665245509.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1517811665245509.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;40.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;吴文广先生就大健康产业趋势，国家战略发展方向的新指引，作了深入浅出的剖析&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;在会上，吴文广先生首先对各位莅临到场祝贺的嘉宾，致以最诚挚的感谢！随后，就国家实施大健康产业趋势，结合富迪在新时代下跟随国家战略发展方向的新指引，作了深入浅出的剖析。他说道：“当下国家重视大健康产业，而我们未来也将大部分重心倾向于这，抵制以药养医，将预防落到实处。打造以“富迪肽”为基础的发展模式。“富迪肽”让我们收获的不仅仅是改变生活质量的机会，更是实现梦想的机会。因为，行业、平台、产品、系统都已打造好。”针对未来发展模式，他解析道，当前富迪占据研发、生产、销售和培训四大基石优势，优质爆品+人性化高效益的互利机制，是收获一众消费者的制胜法宝，也是抵抗竞争对手的最有利方式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180205/1517816715151175.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1517816715151175.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;41.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 24px; line-height: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;叶根女士希望广大经销商在2018从心出发，让爱回家！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;叶根女士致辞时就新常态下战略思想做了深刻的解读，她说道：因为梦想我们欢聚一堂，因为缘份我们终身难忘；因为风雨我们更加坚强，因为坚持我注定辉煌。我们将过剩的生产力、过剩的劳动力释放出去，把消费能力需求、人民的价值观、与一带一路、富迪模式紧密联系在一起，把责任感和使命感重新树立起来，2018从心出发，让爱回家！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wr