rd-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;13&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;日早晨，由富佑集团旗下广州德爱健康管理有限公司举办，为期三天二夜的“四季芳华”生命健康尊享之旅在清远美林湖启幕。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;连续八届荣膺“中国十大慈善家”、&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;中国经济十大商业领袖、中国扶贫开发协会副会长、全国工商联美容化妆品业商会副会长、民建中央对外联络部副部长、广东省第十二届人大代表、富佑集团董事局主席陈怀德先生，连续三届荣膺中国十大慈善家、广东省营养健康产业协会副会长、广东省富迪慈善基金会理事长胡静女士，富迪健康科技有限公司执行总裁吴文广先生，富迪健康科技有限公司健康管理学院执行院长袁伟先生，富迪健康科技有限公司医美事业部总裁林万兴先生，广州德爱健康管理有限公司总裁寇哲先生，德爱健康集团营运副总裁甘萍女士，德爱公司技术顾问孔宪奇先生，德爱集团首席技术专家、湖北医科大学教授毕晓云女士，德爱商学院副院长&lt;/span&gt;Lisa&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;等富佑集团高管，特邀嘉宾国务院中国中医药培训导师、中国涉外教育广州涉外护理学院院长柳金财教授，面部设计首席专家杨欢女士等，以及医美大咖、市场领袖&lt;/span&gt;300&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;多人共同参加了本次活动。活动由资深主持人蓝魏先生主持。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;怀德光日月，母爱化春风&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180530/1527664551237285.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1527664551237285.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;1.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;陈怀德先生回忆起母亲过往&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;启幕式这天正值母亲节，陈怀德先生不禁回忆起了与妈妈的故事，子欲养而亲不待，成功的脚步赶不上爸妈衰老的速度，一幅幅画面仿佛萦绕他脑海、历历在目。因为母亲的过世，让他倍加珍惜身边的人，更加坚定决心让爱的人安享健康。他感慨着现在的人理所应当地接受着母亲给的爱，不知爱有保质期，人也会慢慢消失。正如鱼看不见水，人看不见空气，人们总是习惯至亲的爱，而忽略了她会渐行渐远。远到无法追逐。他说着“不要总在失去之后才懂得珍惜，成长需要代价，但有时候代价太过痛苦，趁现在，多些时间关爱她，陪伴她，把健康带给她。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180530/1527664557123589.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1527664557123589.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;2.webp.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;胡静女士呼吁珍惜身边人&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;对此，一路陪伴陈怀德先生的胡静女士感同身受，深知婆婆是丈夫心里难以释怀的痛，她感慨道，这个世界上所有的爱都指向团聚，唯有父母的爱指向别离，不要让几步的距离，变成浩瀚的海洋，寻不着边际。爱和健康是我们还能在限有的时间追逐的，尽自己所能反哺父母。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max