er-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;陈大陆先生进一步分析爱无价的移动社交电商平台，让直销生活化，让生活直销化。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/uploadfiles/20180530/1527665176683503.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1527665176683503.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;7.webp.jpg&quot; width=&quot;812&quot; height=&quot;523&quot; style=&quot;width: 812px; height: 523px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;寇哲先生阐述健康产业发展趋势&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 29px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;德爱公司总裁寇哲先生，上台阐述了健康产业发展趋势、德爱未来发展战略，打造一流的国际品牌目标。他说道：在技术上，我们有高端合作机构，配置了目前全球顶尖的血液净化免疫激活系统，以干细胞临床转化应用为技术引擎，采用德国第三代纳米血液净化&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;CRRT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;技术；在团队上，拥有国内、国际顶尖血液疗法专家和临床医学专家；硬件上，旗下拥有国际&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;GMP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;标准的细胞实验室、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;&quot;&gt;干细胞提取技术及分子生物实验室，三点合一。势必打造成一家立足于全球的再生医学生态产业平台。他提出，德爱未来的发展趋向，提出以“非视不可、非试不可、非势不可、非是不可”四大理念走创新之路，德爱未来之路必将势不可挡！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0p